OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780078265
OL,3,CFake England shirts seized at car boot
OL,4,Ccould have caught fire
OL,6,FPurchasing fake kits is legal in the
OL,7,FUK, while selling them carries a
OL,8,Fmaximum penalty of 10 years in prison.
OL,10,FTrading Standards team manager Louise
OL,11,FBoyall said "It's the smaller
OL,12,Fretailers on the high street who sell
OL,13,Fthese goods.
OL,15,F"Counterfeiting does fund organised
OL,16,Fcrime and illegal activity, and we
OL,17,Ffind that there are workers who are
OL,18,Fexploited."
